{"type": "article", "id": 36951, "title": "Tiffany换艺术总监，以及， All Star的百年纪念款像个⚾️ | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-01-18T03:13:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 264, "name": "MUJI"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 978, "name": "Raf Simons"}, {"id": 1586, "name": "旅行箱"}, {"id": 1864, "name": "Tiffany"}, {"id": 2145, "name": "Converse"}, {"id": 3133, "name": "Jil Sander"}, {"id": 6424, "name": "Nine West"}, {"id": 10763, "name": "CLOT"}, {"id": 15944, "name": "The Limited"}, {"id": 9116, "name": "Francesca Amfitheatrof"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170118093838ZJjnbwO8zNqi7We5.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/tiffany-appoints-reed-krakoff-as-chief-artistic-officer\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Tiffany 换艺术总监</b></a> |  Reed Krakoff 将于 2 月 1 日正式任职\r\n\r\n Tiffany 的艺术总监。此前，他曾参与重新推出 Tiffany 的家居和配饰系列。Tiffany 的前任艺术总监 Francesca Amfitheatrof 曾为 Tiffany 效力了三年半，并推出了 Tifffany T 系列，带领 Tiffany 进入了一个新的时代。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/the-limited-files-ch-11-petition-inks-25-8m-sycamore-partners-ip-bankruptcy-10753116/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国服装连锁品牌 The Limited 要卖 IP</b></a> | 之前我们曾报道过，因为业绩不好，The Limited 关闭了它在美国的所有门店。日前，The Limited 与私募股权公司签署协议，后者将以 2580 万美元的价格，收购 The Limited 品牌的知识产权。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://finance.yahoo.com/news/nine-west-holdings-acquire-kasper-200300403.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国 Nine West 公司要买做女装的 Kasper </b></a>| Nine West 是世界最大女装皮鞋设计、制造、销售商之一，日前，它宣布要收购美国女装公司 Kasper。Nine West 的首席执行官 Ralph Schipani 称，“ Kasper 是美国女性运动装市场的领导者。”&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/retail/lvmh-said-plotting-e-commerce-thrust-via-le-bon-marche-10748245/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>LVMH 要开电商</b></a> | 据 WWD 报道，LVMH 将以旗下百货公司 Le Bon Marché 的官网为基础翻新自己的线上销售业务。该官网的新版本将于今年年中上线，Céline、Fendi、Louis Vuitton 等之前很少或未在线销售的品牌将上线。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><font color=\"#333332\" size=\"4\">陈冠希的品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/edison-chen-clot-x-absolut-capsule\" rel=\"nofollow\">CLOT 与瑞典品牌 Absolut 合作，打造了一个限量系列</a>。该系列共有两款连帽衫，分别印有蓝色的 </font>SPIRITS ARE RELATIVE 字样和迷幻银色镜面图案。棒球帽上的 A 字与 CLOT 标志结合的白色刺绣 logo，与连帽衫袖子上的细节相呼应。目前已于 Absolut 官网独家发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><font style=\"text-align: justify;\"></font><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104044QGT5UN2p6Mlnqm0i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104057bj3Gv6KZwar7SiO9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104058QU1iNl96SOuEhsBp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104059sP6cXnfH8bFaSU5k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104105Otlp0ciKCkd4hFWJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104107ZcL7ilnkdFv5hGyx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><font style=\"text-align: justify;\">为庆祝 Converse All Star 正式发表 100 周年，从今年起，将有一系列 All Star 100 纪念鞋款陆续登场。在首发的</font><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/converse-all-star-100\" style=\"text-align: justify;\" rel=\"nofollow\"><font color=\"#333332\" size=\"4\"> </font>ALL STAR 100 BASEBALL HI/OX</a><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"> 里，以经典象牙白为底色，搭配红色的棒球双缝线设计，并有高筒和低筒两款。是不是很像⚾️⚾️？</span></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104028v7mcLQqG6hAo028V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104028cvHewXVuZpN4IGqK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667488\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701181040282sT1mMj0reAP8OoJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104034QK0kRyogvUtNe9JI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667213\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/raf-simons-oversized-white-sweater\" rel=\"nofollow\">Raf Simons </a>将 2016 年的 oversized 系列延续到了 2017 年，在这一次发售的全新针织衫里，采用了未处理的下摆和车线细节搭配肩膀处的纽扣，售价为 985 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104000vctLi4KkUFm3r8x1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104013lBmzf97QViyXv8I3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104020y7nAU1djGOgEJfXi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104020ABKT3toyGWhlEY9V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>极简主义的代表 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/jil-sander-mens-2017-fall-winter-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jil Sander 的 2017 秋冬系列</a>，继续 Class for all 的概念，并以小说《Independent People》为灵感，特别使用了来自冰岛的高级羊毛。来看：&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104116ibcHt1dfrFAjepaL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104116tTKsNU3F7bBD1Zfv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104116zEIu03L75qwcCeJU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104116XDgmGJQ1uLwvcTaN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104116emg7bGEtaV061PW5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104117nJDrmIaKMXqj0tPe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104116MGeolwTCWNfUKPpx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104118xkvmJlgoVFSuaqsU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104118O9o6ajiKz3D5udVA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://popbee.com/lifestyle/travel/muji-japan-aluminium-luggage/\" rel=\"nofollow\">MUJI 推出铝制外壳旅行箱</a>，并搭配了双重密码锁，取代了拉链的设计。该旅行箱共有 34L 和 60L 两种尺寸，售价分别为&nbsp;69,000 及 89,000 日元，已于日本率先发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104707TzLyORIVjwBqs6vH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104719PBVGncq8DXk5ajir.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104719d6AgKBNzauWesM4k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104719Leb5AP6NCYhOZgnJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701181047194TbrcCRkKMlifAn0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701181047191PVrGQq5HshcINyM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118104720Myh8nHlim1IEZUuk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/edison-chen-clot-x-absolut-capsule\" rel=\"nofollow\">hypebeast</a></p>"}